name: Chibeast #5/25
description:
Chibeast is a collection of monsters chibi based on fantasy dungeon creature in RPG. And every piece is manually crafted pixel art. 

This collection has dungeon-dwelling monsters such as Orcs, Goblins, Skeletons and some Minotaurs. 

This collection is Suitable for TCG (Trading Card Game), Game Battler Sprite or your D&D Session avatar.
